desmoj.core.simulator

Class ParameterManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • desmoj.core.simulator.ParameterManager
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ExperimentParameterManager, ModelParameterManager

    public class ParameterManager
extends java.lang.Object
implements ModelParameterManager, ExperimentParameterManager
    Class to manage parameters. Parameters are values, which affect a simulation- model or an experiment. Model-parameters are model's constants. Experiment- parameters are experiment-constants which can be used in the experiment's model. This class is accessible from Model through the ModelParameterManager-interface to restrict the accessible methods from a model's view. It is accessible from Experiment through the ExperimentParameterManager-interface to restrict the accessible methods from a experiment's view.
    See Also:
    ModelParameterManager, ExperimentParameterManager
